data.description: NW Cape home on an oversized lot! Affordability meets Sustainability with a Whole home Solar system! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home has a great layout with Double door entry into a large living room and a wall of sliders that open to the lanai, expanding the living space. The delightful kitchen offers beautifully hand crated wood cabinets and counters plus New appliances and a fun backsplash to complete the décor. The primary bedroom is a great size with a slider to the lanai and an ensuite bathroom that also features a hand crafted vanity plus a large soaking tub, a huge separate shower and a private toilet room. Split bedrooms for privacy with a large 2nd bedroom and the 3rd has nice built in shelving. The guest bathroom is beautifully updated and also leads to the lanai. The laundry room has full size front load washer & dryer and the same beautiful crafted wood counter. Feel like you are in your private oasis lounging in the lanai overlooking the lush landscaped yard. Triple lot with a shelled drive for your extra toys or boat storage. Lots of room for a pool too! Enjoy a new roof from 2022 and New electrical 2022. Buyer to qualify for remaining solar balance. Ask for details.
